                <h1>Effective Foreground Examples for Impactful Design</h1>
                <p>Foreground examples illustrate subjects that stand out prominently in a visual composition. Common instances include a vibrant flower in front of a blurred garden or a sharp building silhouette against a sunset. These foreground elements draw the viewer's eye, creating depth and interest in photography, design, or art, enhancing overall engagement.</p>
